        "content": "<div class=\"spoiler-block\"><div class=\"spoiler-header\">\n</div><div class=\"spoiler-content\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<p>example {α : Type _} [Ring α] : OfNat α 0 := inferInstance -- failed to synthesize instance OfNat α 0<br>\nexample {α : Type _} [Ring α] : OfNat α 1 := inferInstance -- failed to synthesize instance OfNat α 1</p>\n</div></div>\n<p>I don't pretend to understand how that is internally consistent...</p>",
